show.description: In a world where power and deception rule, Sarah, a simple girl is forced into a royal game of identities and betrayal. A wrongful prison sentence, a lost child, and a shocking engagement twist set the stage for revenge. Supreme Beauty is a storm of drama, mystery, and hidden truths. Watch Now
